Kalabash
========

*************
Main features
*************

* Administration panel
* Reputation protection: DNSBL checks, DMARC reports and more
* Amavis frontend
* Webmail
* Calendar
* Address book
* Per-user Sieve filters
* Autoreply messages for Postfix
* Graphical statistics about email traffic



